{"tid":2034120,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"串謀獲試題案 蕭源被判14個月","createTime":"2020-05-25T05:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T11:29:28.000Z","uid":225567,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"769b43d7e4f87a930f1ac6ad863559031c0463e9","tid":2034120,"uid":225567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"著名中文科補習導師蕭源，被指串謀2名擔任中學文憑試中國語文科口試主考員的大學同學，分別使他們向蕭洩露試題和評分準則，以供蕭在Facebook發布試題和應考策略，3人早前被裁定兩項串謀公職人員行為失當罪罪成，蕭源今(25日)在屯門法院被判監14個月，另外二人則分別被判監8個月，以及監禁5個月緩刑兩年。<br />\n3名被告包括蕭志勇（即蕭源，42歲）、張國權（43歲）、吳宏樑（43歲）。蕭在案發時是現代教育的中國語文科導師，張、吳分別在佛教沈香林紀念中學和香港華仁書院任教中文科。<br />\n<br />\n蕭和張被控於2016年3月10日至22日，串謀使張蓄意向蕭披露口試試題。蕭與吳則被控於2017年3月1日至9日，串謀使吳蓄意向蕭披露該科的評分準則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fbkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f17a6b4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n要坐仲可以笑到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7f3bad970f7d6ab945ba13dc1025c51ddae9e7","tid":2034120,"uid":225567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"燒完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7220ab9f5804902b0460465e1154454579b917fa","tid":2034120,"uid":46910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"坐14個月 賺到笑"},{"pid":"f78f01425978ef24db7898085fcba448a39b73e4","tid":2034120,"uid":6115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"賺夠了，坐下休息下"},{"pid":"8a43425ae01ba5a81d3b5fcd92530ff4afa9f4dc","tid":2034120,"uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"r